{"tid":2506423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年 7.1 天橋拋「一国兩制」單張　女文員簽保守行為　警誡下稱「支持一國一制喎」","createTime":"2021-04-27T09:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T10:11:39.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5acea014396f283cf56028d6bf37b01c32c2fa19","tid":2506423,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"去年《港區國安法》正式生效當天，民陣發起的七一遊行被禁止，當日逾 300 人被捕。一名女文員被指在<span class=\"red\">天橋拋下單張，導致交通受阻</span>，被控在公眾地方犯的妨擾罪。案件今（27日）於東區裁判法院提堂，控方同意自簽守行為撤回控罪，最終主任裁判官羅德泉頒令被告自簽 1000 元，守行為 24 個月。<br />\n<br />\n警員搜查後發現在被告的手袋內有 57 張印有「一国兩制」及「ONE COUNTRY TWONE SYSTEMs」的紅色單張，以公眾妨擾罪拘捕她，警誡下被告表示「係呀！我支持一國一制喎」。"},{"pid":"2936fd624a9eeb33cb0252ca2c5ffe4c7ae07052","tid":2506423,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4-7-1-%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E6%8B%8B-%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-%E5%96%AE%E5%BC%B5-%E5%A5%B3%E6%96%87%E5%93%A1%E7%B0%BD%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%A1%E4%B8%8B%E7%A8%B1-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%88%B6%E5%96%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4-7-1-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%258B%258B-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%25BC%25B5-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%25A1%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2596%258E%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=4abd3c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4-7-1-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%258B%258B-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%2585%25A9%2